Chavez Says He Is on the Path to a Full Recovery

-- B y   C h a r l i e   D e v e r e u x
-- 
2011-09-29T11:57:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/chavez-says-he-is-on-the-path-to-a-full-recovery.html
Venezuela ’s President  Hugo Chavez 
said he’s on the path to a full recovery and will resume his
normal working routine soon.  Chavez, in a telephone interview broadcast on state
television, said Venezuelans should disregard rumors about his
health after Miami-based newspaper El Nuevo Herald reported he
had been hospitalized with kidney failure.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
